    "body": "Hi guys, just wanted to let you know we've successfully exposed custom page sizes via `web_contents.js` without any side-effects as far as we can tell. How do you feel about going rogue and exposing it before there's explicit support in Chromium? (+ maybe include a disclaimer in the docs)\n"
